::Feline::

She went alone the corridoor and went along to map out the ship as 
she walked along.  She came to the Quarters section.  She mapped out 
where the rooms where in relation to other parts of the she had been 
to already.   She went futher down and came to the lab area.  She 
walked into the room and looked around.  She saw the tables and other 
work benches.  She saw the autoguns in the celing.  She saw the CR 
chambers just in the next room.  She smiled, she had been here 
before.  She walked back into the hallway.   She saw a stairwell 
going downward.  She decided to expoler the ship and hat was what she 
was going to do.  She walked down the stairs towards what parts of 
the ship, she didn't know.  she found herself walking along part of 
the engine room.  She smiled and mapped, in her memory banks, all 
that she could see.  She kept walking and looking.  If someone caught 
her, she would just say she was lost. After all, she as new to the 
ship, she thought.
